high_descs: Turn left  cross the room then turn right go to the desk
Pick up the credit card on the edge of the desk
Look up and face the bowl on the desk
Put the credit card in the bowl on the same desk
Pick up the bowl with credit card
Turn right then head to the right side of the study table
Put the bowl with credit card on the study table
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with credit card on the study table

high_descs: Turn around and take two steps then turn right to walk to the desk with a light on it.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you.
Look up at the bowl near the wall.
Put the credit card in the bowl near the wall.
Pick up the bowl with the credit card in it.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the right side of the desk and stand facing it to the left of the alarm clock.
Put the bowl on the desk slightly to the right of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a credit card in it on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small desk on the right.
Pick up the credit card in front of the pencil.
Look at the back of the desk.
Put the credit card in the bowl to the left of the lamp.
Pick up the bowl from the desk.
Walk over to the right side of the desk to the right.
Put the glass bowl on the desk to the left of the keys.
anns.task_desc: To put a credit card in a bowl and put the bowl on the desk.
